OL,3,CCaroline Flack's mother: There's no
OL,4,Ccomeback on newspapers if they tell
OL,5,Cuntruths
OL,7,FCaroline Flack's mother has explored
OL,8,Fwhy her daughter felt like she had no
OL,9,Fchoice but to take her own life in a
OL,10,Fnew documentary, ITV News
OL,11,FEntertainment Correspondent Rishi
OL,12,FDavda reports
OL,14,FWhen TV presenter Caroline Flack took
OL,15,Fher own life in February 2020, her
OL,16,Fmother Christine was left asking why.
OL,18,FNot why she did it, but rather why
OL,19,Fothers acted in a way that left the 40-
OL,20,Fyear-old feeling like she had no other
OL,21,Fchoice.
