OL,3,CCaroline Flack's mother: There's no
OL,4,Ccomeback on newspapers if they tell
OL,5,Cuntruths
OL,7,FAt the time, she was facing
OL,8,Fprosecution for allegedly assaulting
OL,9,Fher boyfriend. Now, more than five
OL,10,Fyears later, Christine is releasing a
OL,11,Fdocumentary about her daughter's final
OL,12,Fdays.
OL,14,FReflecting on the process of reliving
OL,15,Fthe most traumatic moment of her life,
OL,16,FChristine said: "It's given me clarity
OL,17,Fbut hasn't given me closure, and I
OL,18,Fthink that is the hardest thing."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
