OL,3,CCaroline Flack's mother: There's no
OL,4,Ccomeback on newspapers if they tell
OL,5,Cuntruths
OL,7,FFollowing that arrest, the Crown
OL,8,FProsecution Service initially decided
OL,9,Fthat the star should receive a caution.
OL,11,FHowever, a Metropolitan Police officer
OL,12,Fappealed that decision, and she was
OL,13,Fcharged with assault by beating.
OL,15,FIt was later ruled, by a coroner, that
OL,16,FCaroline Flack had killed herself
OL,17,Fbecause of her prosecution and the
OL,18,Fpublicity she feared the trial would
OL,19,Fattract.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
