OL,3,CCaroline Flack's mother: There's no
OL,4,Ccomeback on newspapers if they tell
OL,5,Cuntruths
OL,7,FChristine believes Caroline was
OL,8,Ftreated differently because of her
OL,9,Ffame and spent four years trying to
OL,10,Ffind out the chain of events that led
OL,11,Fto the passing of one of her four
OL,12,Fchildren.
OL,14,F"When I first started, it was two
OL,15,Fyears before I got any answers. It's
OL,16,Fvery hard to get to speak to anybody
OL,17,Fat the top or to take it any further,"
OL,18,Fshe said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
