OL,3,CCaroline Flack's mother: There's no
OL,4,Ccomeback on newspapers if they tell
OL,5,Cuntruths
OL,7,F"That's the media, the police, the
OL,8,FCPS. You get so far and they say
OL,9,Fsorry, but that was it."
OL,11,FFollowing reviews and an inquest into
OL,12,Ftheir actions, the Met Police said
OL,13,Fthat the outcomes "did not find any
OL,14,Fmisconduct for any officer, including
OL,15,Fin relation to the decision to appeal
OL,16,Fthe CPS outcome."
OL,18,F"Organisational learning was
OL,19,Fidentified, around record-keeping and
OL,20,Fdocumentation of decision-making...
OL,21,FThese have since been addressed."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
