OL,3,CCaroline Flack's mother: There's no
OL,4,Ccomeback on newspapers if they tell
OL,5,Cuntruths
OL,7,FWhile the CPS asserted, "We are
OL,8,Fsatisfied that the prosecution was
OL,9,Fcorrectly brought."
OL,11,FBut when Christine is asked how those
OL,12,Fstatements make her feel, she told me,
OL,13,F"It's mixed, I'm angry because it
OL,14,Fshouldn't have happened."
OL,16,FAs someone in the spotlight for many
OL,17,Fyears, Caroline had become accustomed
OL,18,Fto her life being used to fill columns
OL,19,Fof newspapers and posts on social
OL,20,Fmedia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
