OL,3,CCaroline Flack's mother: There's no
OL,4,Ccomeback on newspapers if they tell
OL,5,Cuntruths
OL,7,FHowever, following her arrest, she
OL,8,Fdominated front pages and was subject
OL,9,Fto abuse and hateful messages online.
OL,11,FChristine doesn't believe that the way
OL,12,Fwe treat people in the public eye has
OL,13,Fchanged since Caroline's death.
OL,15,F"Not at all," she says, "all attention
OL,16,Fis fine, they're in the public eye,
OL,17,Fbut it has got to be checked and it
OL,18,Fhas got to be true.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
