OL,3,CCaroline Flack's mother: There's no
OL,4,Ccomeback on newspapers if they tell
OL,5,Cuntruths
OL,7,F"There is no comeback on newspapers if
OL,8,Fthey tell untruths, as long as they
OL,9,Fsay a source has told them, they can
OL,10,Fwrite what they like."
OL,12,F"Anybody can comment on it, with the
OL,13,Fmost awful comments, and that hurts,
OL,14,Fthat really hurts people."
OL,16,FCaroline Flack: Search For The Truth
OL,17,Fis out on Disney+ on November 10.
OL,19,FChristine hopes it'll leave a lasting
OL,20,Fimpact on all of those who watch it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
